{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Slice___Dice_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slice through your enemies. Parry, dash, and utilize colorful abilities to dispatch your foes. Dismember them into a cascade of colorful blood!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/SliceDice-ezgif.com-overlay.gif?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Brutal_Bosses_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Disembowel a gauntlet of bosses with unique move-sets, weapons, and abilities. Spears, guns, and chainsaws stand little chance against your trusty katana.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/BrutalBossesClip-ezgif.com-overlay__1_.gif?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Open_World_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paint a small open world with blood and graffiti. Vibe out to lo-fi samurai tunes. Together with your young companion, complete quests across multiple biomes. Journey through bustling towns, bamboo forests, crystal caves, rock and roll raves, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/OpenWorldClip-ezgif.com-overlay__1_.gif?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Story_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ren, in the face of an impossible order, cuts down his Shogun in cold blood. Alongside the baby he refused to kill, the duo makes their escape and settles into a normal life. As time passes, Ren waits anxiously for his past to catch up to him.     <br> <br>Years later, the Shogun's children seek revenge for the death of their father - not only on Ren, but on the young boy he cares for.  <br> <br>Hunt them down and slice their throats before they get the chance.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728590462","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/page.bg.jpg?t=1728590462","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/abd19a562ec904aaedc59b4fd6f5b5863f0bd414/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728590462","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/abd19a562ec904aaedc59b4fd6f5b5863f0bd414/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728590462","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Slice___Dice_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slice through your enemies. Parry, dash, and utilize colorful abilities to dispatch your foes. Dismember them into a cascade of colorful blood!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/SliceDice-ezgif.com-overlay.gif?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Brutal_Bosses_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Disembowel a gauntlet of bosses with unique move-sets, weapons, and abilities. Spears, guns, and chainsaws stand little chance against your trusty katana.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/BrutalBossesClip-ezgif.com-overlay__1_.gif?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Open_World_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Paint a small open world with blood and graffiti. Vibe out to lo-fi samurai tunes. Together with your young companion, complete quests across multiple biomes. Journey through bustling towns, bamboo forests, crystal caves, rock and roll raves, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/OpenWorldClip-ezgif.com-overlay__1_.gif?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/extras/Story_Banner.png?t=1728590462\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ren, in the face of an impossible order, cuts down his Shogun in cold blood. Alongside the baby he refused to kill, the duo makes their escape and settles into a normal life. As time passes, Ren waits anxiously for his past to catch up to him.     <br> <br>Years later, the Shogun's children seek revenge for the death of their father - not only on Ren, but on the young boy he cares for.  <br> <br>Hunt them down and slice their throats before they get the chance.</p>","developers":["Studio Yarn"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2684950/header.jpg?t=1728590462","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"name":"Colorful Katana","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul c